Based on the draft Consumer Privacy Bill of Rights, this establishes the chain:<br> CONSUMER <<<- Privacy Policy <<- CPBR <- EXPERTS and STAKEHOLDERS  <br>Iteration will establish:<br> CONSUMER ->>> Privacy Policy ->> CPBR -> EXPERTS and STAKEHOLDERS<br>Interactive, distributed regulation.<br>It will also involve tying this in with requirements of other countries, US States, and specified industries.  Anything that affects what a company can or must do with information must be expressed for the company's own purposes their relationships. It should be crowd-source, from experts and stakeholders such as regulators. 
